{"lastModified":1773136893089,"uri":"c::7819198774::vessel::dec9f3e0-dbeb-11f0-8dcf-91f8ea34d139","yachtType":["Motor"],"description":"Operating Area: Fiji, Whitsundays, Australia\nHome Port: South Pacific\n\nBrand new and built to impress, PAZIENZA is a 34.9m explorer yacht from Cantiere delle Marche that redefines what it means to travel well. Delivered in 2024 and designed by Francesco Paszkowski, she’s a standout new build with serious presence. Her layout has been thoughtfully designed to create a calm, flowing onboard experience. A master suite on the main deck, VIP on the upper, and four guest cabins below make it work just\nas well for families as it does for friends or charter groups. From the warm, layered interiors to the wide-open aft decks made for entertaining, Pazienza feels like a boutique hotel that moves with you. She’s built for long-range cruising, with the space, stability and setup to make longer trips feel easy. Outside, the decks are made for entertaining – long lunches, golden hour drinks and those moments when no one wants the day to end.\nPazienza is for those who want more than just a yacht. They want the feeling that comes with it","blueprint":{"name":"PAZIENZA","images":["/media/media::image::a::vessel::dec9f3e0-dbeb-11f0-8dcf-91f8ea34d139::assets::985e89f0-dbed-11f0-a003-43346cf82ee7/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::dec9f3e0-dbeb-11f0-8dcf-91f8ea34d139::assets::9868c320-dbed-11f0-b443-61339ebdcb68/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::dec9f3e0-dbeb-11f0-8dcf-91f8ea34d139::assets::986344e0-dbed-11f0-b442-61339ebdcb68/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::dec9f3e0-dbeb-11f0-8dcf-91f8ea34d139::assets::98636bf0-dbed-11f0-b442-61339ebdcb68/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::dec9f3e0-dbeb-11f0-8dcf-91f8ea34d139::assets::98667930-dbed-11f0-b443-61339ebdcb68/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::dec9f3e0-dbeb-11f0-8dcf-91f8ea34d139::assets::9863e120-dbed-11f0-b442-61339ebdcb68/{ima